@Qwertide.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5229

### Top leaderboard entries
GET {{Qwertide.Api_HostAddress}}/api/scores?top=10
Accept: application/json

### Submit a score
POST {{Qwertide.Api_HostAddress}}/api/scores
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerName": "kayl_okafor",
  "wpm": 138,
  "accuracy": 98.1,
  "durationSecs": 21.4,
  "passageId": 1
}

